  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n                        \u003cp\u003eIn the center of Vietnam’s Tiền Giang province, \u003ca href=\"https://archiro.vn/portfolio/noahsnest-project/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eNoah’s Nest\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e is a modern home steeped in tradition. Designed by \u003ca href=\"https://archiro.vn/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eArchiro Vietnam\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/a\u003e for acclaimed actor Lâm Thanh Nhã, this compact yet thoughtfully envisioned residence gracefully fuses local heritage with contemporary architectural ideals.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=582145\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-582145\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-2-810x1215.jpg\" alt=\"Indoor space with green plants in a corner, a green and brick wall, tiled floor, wooden table and chairs, and two hanging light bulbs from a woven ceiling.\" width=\"810\" height=\"1215\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-2-810x1215.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-2-800x1200.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-2-768x1152.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-2-1024x1536.jpg 1024w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-2.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBuilt with a modest 603-square-foot layout, Noah’s Nest is designed to honor the owner’s roots while leaning into modern Vietnamese architecture. Rather than relying on imported, industrial materials, the home showcases locally sourced elements such as baked clay bricks, bamboo poles, straw mats traditionally used in rice storage, and ornamental stone mortars. These choices go beyond aesthetic appeal – they ground the home in the cultural fabric of the Mekong Delta, paying tribute to Tiền Giang’s agricultural identity.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=582146\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-582146\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-3-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"A modern kitchen and dining area features a black spiral staircase, indoor plants, brick walls, and natural light from large windows and a glass door.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-3-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-3-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-3-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-3.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe deliberate contrast between rustic textures and clean, modern lines creates a space that feels both familiar and fresh. This balance between tradition and modernity allows the home to blend into its rural surroundings while asserting its unique architectural identity.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=582147\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-582147\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-4-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"An open kitchen and dining area with wooden and bamboo decor, large windows, hanging lights, and a view of a garden with a bicycle outside.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-4-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-4-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-4-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-4.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eDespite its compact interior space, the home is designed to feel open and expansive, thanks to strategic skylights and integrated greenery. Natural ventilation flows freely through the structure, reducing reliance on artificial cooling in the tropical climate. Indoor plants and outdoor views are incorporated throughout the layout, emphasizing biophilic design and fostering a healthier living environment.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=582148\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-582148\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-5-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"A person prepares coffee in a modern kitchen with brick walls, open shelving, pendant lights, and a large window.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-5-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-5-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-5-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-5.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe philosophy behind Noah’s Nest extends beyond materials and form. With its unfinished walls and open windows, it’s a living structure – one that, like a nest, requires attention, love, and shared responsibility. These intentional imperfections give the home character and remind its inhabitants of the evolving nature of family life.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=582149\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-582149\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-6-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"A kitchen with wooden cabinets and a stone countertop looks out through a large, irregular brick-framed window onto a courtyard with a bicycle, plants, and a striped metal gate.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-6-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-6-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-6-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-6.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=582150\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-582150\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-7-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"A hallway with exposed brick walls, wooden doors, a wooden bench with decorative items, and a painting, next to a black metal railing and a window.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-7-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-7-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Resi