an open hallway leading to another room with a plant and painting.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-9-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-9-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-9-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-9.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=582153\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-582153\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-10-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"A modern bedroom with a bed, green bedding, a freestanding bathtub on pebbles, large windows with white curtains, and plants; a person stands near the balcony door.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-10-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-10-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-10-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-10.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eA unique feature throughout the home is its use of integrated indoor rock beds, which serve both functional and aesthetic purposes. On the ground floor, a rock garden anchors the open-plan living area, wrapping around a spiral staircase that leads to the upper level. This sculptural focal point is softened by lush greenery, blurring the lines between architecture and nature. Upstairs, a second rock bed becomes the base for a floating bathtub, positioned directly across from the bed in the spacious primary suite. Enveloped by tropical plants and natural textures, the bathing area feels like a private spa retreat – bringing tranquility and biophilic design into the heart of the home.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=582154\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-582154\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-11-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"A modern bathroom with a freestanding tub, indoor plants, a wooden chair, exposed brick walls, and sheer curtains by a sliding door leading to a balcony.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-11-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-11-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-11-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-11.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=582155\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-582155\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-12-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"A bedroom with a large bed, open book, freestanding bathtub, potted plants, sheer curtains, and exposed brick walls under a woven ceiling with hanging light bulbs.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-12-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-12-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-12-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-12.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=582156\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-582156\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-13-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"A silver bicycle with a front basket is parked against a wall with a large, irregular hole exposing brickwork, next to potted green plants on a tiled floor.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-13-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-13-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-13-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-13.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=582157\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-582157\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-14-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"A modern patio with potted plants, a gravel walkway, and a bicycle leaning against a wall featuring a large round window with exposed brick edges.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-14-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-14-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-14-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-14.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=582158\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-582158\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-15-810x452.jpg\" alt=\"Potted green plants on a wooden deck next to a brick and metal fence with an open gate, casting striped shadows on gravel ground.\" width=\"810\" height=\"452\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-15-810x452.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-15-800x446.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-15-768x428.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-15.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe home’s exposed brick construction is the result of close collaboration between the design team and local craftsmen. This technique not only highlights the tactile beauty of handmade materials but also optimizes building efficiency and cost. By showcasing the natural tones and patterns of the bricks, the home gains visual warmth while reducing the need for added ornamentation. Hidden within the brickwork are structural components, skillfully integrated to give the illusion of simplicity while offering robust support.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=582159\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-582159\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-16-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"Two-story brick house with large windows and a gated entrance, featuring greenery in the front yard and two people visible, one upstairs and one downstairs.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-16-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-16-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-16-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-16.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=582160\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-582160\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-17-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"A modern house with brick and metal fencing stands beside a muddy, narrow road at dusk, with visible power lines overhead and neighboring buildings nearby.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-17-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-17-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-17-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-17.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=582161\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-582161\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-18-810x540.jpg\" alt=\"Two-story modern brick house with a black gate and balcony, exterior lights on, situated along a muddy dirt road with a fenced-off garden area.\" width=\"810\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-18-810x540.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-18-800x533.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-18-768x512.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-18.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=582162\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-582162\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-19-810x535.jpg\" alt=\"Architectural sketch of a modern building with curved elements, a sloped roof, a patch of grass, and a tree, drawn in pencil and colored pencil.\" width=\"810\" height=\"535\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-19-810x535.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-19-800x528.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-19-768x507.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-19.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003ca href=\"https://design-milk.com/?attachment_id=582163\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-582163\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-20-810x590.jpg\" alt=\"An open sketchbook shows a pencil drawing of a modern house and trees, surrounded by colored pencils and a sharpener on a wooden desk.\" width=\"810\" height=\"590\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-20-810x590.jpg 810w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-20-800x583.jpg 800w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-20-768x560.jpg 768w, https://design-milk.com/images/2025/07/Noahs-Nest-Residence-Archiro-Vietnam-20.jpg 1280w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 810px) 100vw, 810px\"/\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eFor more information on Noah’s Nest and Archiro Vietnam, visit \u003ca href=\"https://archiro.vn/portfolio/noahsnest-project/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener external noreferrer\" data-wpel-link=\"external\"\u003earchiro.vn\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003ePhotography by Dat Bui.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n                        \n                                                    \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2021/11/Caroline-Williamson-100x100.jpg\" srcset=\"https://design-milk.com/images/2021/11/Caroline-Williamson.jpg 2x\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\" alt=\"\"/\u003e                                    \u003c/p\u003e\n                                \u003c/div\u003e\n\n                                \u003cdiv\u003e\n                                    \u003cp\u003eCaroline Williamson is Editor-in-Chief of Design Milk. She has a BFA in photography from SCAD and can usually be found searching for vintage wares, doing New York Times crossword puzzles in pen, or reworking playlists on Spotify.\u003c/p\u003e\n                                    \n                                \u003c/div\u003e\n                            \u003c/div\u003e\n                                            \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
